FBIS3-16934 "drsov055_b_94020" FBIS-SOV-94-055 Document Type:Daily Report 22 Mar 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Military, Nuclear & Space Issues Grachev Hopes for Defense Budget Increase PM2203131594 Moscow ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA in Russian 22 Mar 94 First Edition p 3 PM2203131594 Moscow ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Unattributed report: "Grachev Expects Money"] [Text] The Russian Federation defense minister has voiced the hope that the ministry's budget for 1994 will nonetheless be increased. The defense minister noted that the proposed total defense budget (37 trillion rubles) is being insisted on solely by the Finance Ministry. In his opinion, it would meet only 46-47 percent of the Armed Forces' requirements.
